This paper describes a new database architecture that aims to improve performance in high load situations by batching queries and sharing computation across concurrent queries and updates. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the database (cs.DB), distributed computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), operating systems (cs.OS), or performance (cs.PF) sub-categories.
